::Shredder/Zardus::

Shredder chuckles. "I've been a predacon for a long time now," he says to 
Sinesis,  "And almost every bot I've met that was as stupid as you, I saw 
die. If you keep bragging about how many bounties lie on your head, you'll 
get killed pretty soon..."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus nods. "Good. We have a lab. You can use it if needed."
